			>
			<div>since necros often take up the role of mana battery in most groups and raids, have a way where we can visually see how much mana our target has with out haveing to go &quot;how is your mana&quot; every 2 mins.......my second idea is change up how sacrifice works, currently the mein use for it is the ee's for rezing people.....i have found very few necros that use any of the other spells that require EE's. For us EE's are rather expensive to make.... the only way we get some if a) we have a bot that is high enough in lvl to sac, b) get lucky and some guy just wants to lvl down fast....or c) pay an arm and leg to let someone sec them a few times.........in most cases its c. some of use are rather to broke to do that so we a are stuck with no EE's. i suggest a way to use sacrifice on npc mobs, if it is successfuly we get the ee but no xp, if you make it this easy for us to make ee's i wont care if they become no trade or not......well thats my ideas to help us out a little and even make us of some of those ee spells you gave us</div>	
