<P>with mind rack with the 4 tick recorse they will get 600 mana in one minute at the cost of 600 mana... this is a one to one mana ratio and get about 60 mana a tic.... recast time is one minute</P>
<P>mind flay with the 4 tic recorse gives 720 mana and cost 700 mana...little better than 1 to 1 ration.....72 mana a tic for the 1 minute recast time....</P>
<P>now efficiency is dependent on what you want to be efficiant at.....in one minute twiching can almost double the the amount of mana put out compaired to the mana draining spells.&nbsp; but if you want to be efficant in mana the mana drains are one to one ration to amount of mana to get and to cast.......</P>
<P>but mana draining does have its up and downs...it gives all in the group mana and a high mana regen for 4 tics...weather they need it or not....in most cases the only one that needs mana is a healer or chanty when over tasked.&nbsp; mana drains also require a mob with mana to be present with out this the spell is worthless to give mana</P>
<P>to clerics mana ratio is important.....to necros it should not weight as heavily due to our high regen.&nbsp; while you think my way says i love innefficiency and promotes it...you way say " my mana is more important than your mana even though i can regen almost 3 times faster than you while you have mana regen buffs"</P>
<P>...as far as meding goes i med after i dot so i am almost never under 50% mana</P>	
