<P>actually i did the math very well...and i did take in accoutn necros do get the recourse. it cost necros 600 mana to cast mind rack all get 300 back from the instint part of the spell, we got that too.&nbsp; then all get a recorse with is adds 75 mana per tick up to 4 ticks...that equals 300 mana....so 300+300= 600.&nbsp; check allah if you dont believe me</P>
<P>and since you cant cast that for an other min it...which is 60s...6 ticks....600mana/6ticks= 10mana per tick</P>
<P>and as far as my math work is going i am not including the dps because i am sticktly working with the mana giving in this matter. also stacking many dots also takes some time often i am with others that drop mobs less than 45 so why stack 5 or more dots when the last dots get one maybe two ticks...that is wasting mana....</P>
<P>and no i guild does not get mad when i am sitting... for one simple fact.....mana regen is better when sitting than standing...</P>
<P>and most of the time i am grouped with a shamy and a cleric and thats about it as far as casters go in a group...now why in the hell would i mind rack on chance the mob has mana to give both the cleric and the shammy mana when the shammy can recover mana a whole hell lot faster than i can give it to them</P>
<P>and by the way......if you think necros are only dps...go back and look at your spells again....while most are dps there are still many spells that give necros a utilty belt to fall on as well what good is it when can only cast one line of spell that you only have one of due to mobs high resist in everything but one area</P>
