<P>ps....mind flay cost 700 mana to cost....recorse is up to 4 ticks....everyone 360 mana when it goes off...recorse does 90 mana per tick.....which is a total of 360....360+360= 720 total mana from mind flay...and you cant cast that for another minute...so it gives about 12 mana per tick for 1 minute...dont believe me....got to allah and pull up the spell...and do the math.....and dont forget.....if a group really want super high dps...they could go with a wizard</P>	
